{"tid":1514919,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非入]用memo紙遮cctv鏡頭是合法的","createTime":"2019-08-29T02:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T06:07:58.000Z","uid":287422,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"251fe2b39f20fe2c3f7b931785c751cf1db1ef0a","tid":1514919,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:50:29.000Z","msg":"大家都知現在連地鐵都大把cctv,如果你討厭黨鐵侵犯私隱，但又怕犯法，其實你可以用memo紙遮的，只要你無破壞鏡頭就無犯法。<br />\n<br />\n當個個都這樣做時，成批cctv就等如暫時性廢了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b683276f3fcff28e45a8a7060f61842cbf299b8b","tid":1514919,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:51:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"e121dfca5439d172b8a4f78773090a695fab7517","tid":1514919,"uid":12554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:52:37.000Z","msg":"Duct tape<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b9e479344b61721125223fb1e2366bbe105d75","tid":1514919,"uid":35842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTykUks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTykUks.jpg&h=e262c427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3J6Zqr9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3J6Zqr9.jpg&h=398279dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjFi3Tp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjFi3Tp.jpg&h=1a5d1359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">901 和你塞 13:00 見</span></span> <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithy